Inconsistent logic between `addMapper` and `removeMapper` methods. In `addMapper`, the `handleMapper` call is only executed for non-wildcard mappers (inside the `else` block at line 268), but in `removeMapper` (line 279), `handleMapper` is called for ALL mappers regardless of whether they are wildcard mappers or not. This asymmetry could lead to mappers not being properly removed from the internal collections.

